the diary of anne frank is a 1959 american drama film directed by george stevens and written by frances hyland and albert hackett . the screenplay was written by frances hyland and directed by boris sagal . the screenplay was written by frances hyland and albert hackett . the film was directed by boris ingster and starred millie perkins as anne frank . the film was nominated for three academy awards , including best picture , best director , best supporting actress for her role as anne frank .